videos.headline: New Mexico's Jalen House gets the steal and the score
videos.description: New Mexico guard Jalen House swipes the ball and takes it the other way for the easy score.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (New Mexico’s Jalen House gets the steal and the score) 2022/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ethan Anderson beats the first-half buzzer for Wyoming
videos.description: Wyoming takes the lead before halftime as Ethan Anderson flips in the floater at the buzzer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Ethan Anderson beats the first-half buzzer for Wyoming) 2022/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Josiah Allick flushes home dunk for New Mexico
videos.description: Josiah Allick gives New Mexico a 3-point lead with a two-handed flush.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Josiah Allick flushes home dunk for New Mexico) 2022/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wyoming's Jeremiah Oden flushes the reverse dunk
videos.description: Jeremiah Oden gives Wyoming the lead late with a baseline reverse dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wyoming’s Jeremiah Oden flushes the reverse dunk) 2022/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: New Mexico survives and stays undefeated
videos.description: New Mexico hits two late free throws and gets a couple defensive stops to beat Wyoming to remain undefeated.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (New Mexico survives and stays undefeated) 2022/12/31 ESHEET
